{"tid":526871,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港已死-----100毛譚仔廣告","createTime":"2018-01-12T05:19:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-19T14:02:04.000Z","uid":99805,"like":84,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"585718d2dfd6c441501c256cb4e86f0280a11c12","tid":526871,"uid":99805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T05:19:17.000Z","msg":"100毛放左個新既廣告,內容係用譚仔班大媽做話題<br />\n當中留言全部都係好好笑,好有趣等無營養既留言<br />\n<br />\n香港既死因唔係因為多左班廣東話都未正既大陸人<br />\n而係多得班香港人比人強姦住都覺得好笑<br />\n<br />\n只要有班人用旺角西洋菜街既妖怪做個懶好笑既廣告,自然佢地都會成為香港特色之一"},{"pid":"92cce061c6ab6d60e0ca59c05c2db2aadc5b66f5","tid":526871,"uid":99805,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T05:20:27.000Z","msg":"睇見留言既人咁開心,真係好似一班圈養既豬,笑住食佢地既豬餿"},{"pid":"6662cb97a6187dec46c41ae3144ecd28ce88edf9","tid":526871,"uid":99805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T05:22:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17760e48bdf70394a476e3fd25a36bd7b0347565","tid":526871,"uid":3454,"like":30,"dislike":3,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T05:23:59.000Z","msg":"好似係舊登個陣帶起先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n勿演勿演勿得咁開心"},{"pid":"5de3abfa73e29408e047df698e28bf3b0aecb9f2","tid":526871,"uid":99805,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"17760e48bdf70394a476e3fd25a36bd7b0347565","tid":526871,"uid":3454,"like":30,"dislike":3,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T05:23:59.000Z","msg":"好似係舊登個陣帶起先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n勿演勿演勿得咁開心"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T05:30:57.000Z","msg":"係,我都係入面出過聲,有d舊登巴打當時都有串呢個風氣覺得好笑既人都係無得救<br />\n事實證明香港真係豬多過人"},{"pid":"086a1dc35ba04e9b32a6e32affc1e01909dea59c","tid":526871,"uid":99805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T05:34:18.000Z","msg":"再次REFRESH睇下新留言,都有3幾個巴打出聲<br />\n不過都唔敢講得太直,你知啦,港豬圍起爐上黎真係好恐怖"},{"pid":"2259a063accc9783eb5d1efcd111df92